::DarkMouse::

She went back into the lab and waited for Dracona to wake up.  She 
didn' know why, but the whole situation felt so darned familiar.  She 
saw how Dracona wasn't waking up.  She gave her another injection of 
the antidote.  She knew the drug wouldn't harm her in any way.  But 
she should be waking up very soon.

DarkMouse walked to the door way and looked around the main room of 
the base.  She was wanting to talk to Scorponok.  She wanted to find 
out about her past.  Something that she had forgotten. She knew that 
she was reprogrammed.  But what she was before the reprogramming, she 
had no clue.  And that's what she wanted to ask him.
